# Whitelist (fail-closed): ignore everything, then re-include only what ships in
# the .vsix. vsce reads only .vscodeignore, so a whitelist is expressed by
# ignoring `**` and negating with `!` (matching the include-list style preferred
# in the main ryl repo). New files never ship unless added here.
**
!package.json
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!LICENSE
!dist/extension.js
!images/icon.png
!bundled/**
